rry-shares-music-industry-cheat-codes-she-gave-chappell-roan-and-doechii-for-handling-fame-3833042">凯蒂·佩里（Katy Perry）的邮政音乐行业“作弊代码”，她给了查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）和杜希（Doechii）处理名望，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Katy Perry，Chappel Roan和Doechii。图片来源：丽莎湖，史蒂文·西奥恩（Steven Simione）和迈克尔·洛奇萨诺（Michael Loccisano）" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Katy-Perry-Chappel-Roan-and-Doechii.-Credit-Lisa-Lake-Steven-Simione-and-Michael-Loccisano-via-GETTY-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/Katy-Perry">凯蒂·佩里（Katy Perry）</a>对她的提示和“作弊代码”开放，她在处理名望时给了<a href="/artists/Chappell-Roan">Chappell Roan</a>和<a href="/artists/Doechii">Doechii</a> 。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/katy-perry-every-single-ranked-3776044">凯蒂·佩里（Katy Perry）：按照伟大顺序排名</a></strong></li></ul><p>在对<a href="https://www.rollingstone.com/music/music-features/katy-perry-interview-roan-lifetimes-tour-doechii-chappell-1235247356/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Rolling Stone的</em></a>新采访中，“我吻了一个女孩”的杀手透露，她已经分享了一些有关如何处理名望以及它可能带来的颠簸的知识，并与两种格莱美奖提名的行为带来了。</p><p>在谈到Doechii时，他最近与Perry合作在“我是他的，他是我的”的曲目上时说：“我们进行了很多坦率的对话。我想，“女孩，这是作弊代码。尝试一下。如果您不仅想生存，如果您想壮成长，如果您想在这个身上享受一生，如果您想过人类的体验，而不仅仅是出名并藏在酒店里在某个地方，从来没有真正体验生活的美丽。”</p><p>她继续说：“您总是尊重那些在您面前铺平道路的人。我认为我现在在哪里，我在某些方面很高兴能成为任何人问的人。我对此非常诚实，我也伸出手，只是“嘿，你还好吗？”就像，我在这里。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="凯蒂·佩里（Katy Perry） - 我是他的，他是我的ft。Doechii（官方视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/sH89mSsCTu8?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>罗恩（Roan）此前曾分享过，佩里（Perry）在挣扎着成名时就与她联系。 “红酒超新星”的歌手对她对粉丝文化的看法很开放，并经常<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-chastises-fans-weird-and-creepy-behaviour-thats-not-normal-3785060">诚实地谈到她对明星的迅速上升</a>。去年，她讨论了极端粉丝行为的正常化，她将其描述为“跟踪”和人们“在网上谈论狗屎”，他们“不会让你一个人”。</p><p> She also compared fame to <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-says-fame-is-like-an-abusive-ex-husband-3794622">“an abusive ex-husband”</a> , and took to TikTok to <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-chastises-fans-weird-and-creepy-behaviour-thats-not-normal-3785060">share her thoughts on “weird” and “creepy” followers</a> .然后，她继续提出<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/chappell-roan-writes-to-superfans-about-predatory-behaviour-women-dont-owe-you-shit-3786492">所谓的“超级粉丝”的“掠夺性行为”</a> ，包括“非自愿的身体和社交互动”。</p><p>在被问及与罗恩聊天后，佩里说：“我想，你还好吗？因为这就像一个怪异的实验！并非每个人都承受着这种巨大的压力，在这样的范围内以及如此聚光灯下。这些天，这很快了。它真的被扔进去。” </p><figure id="attachment_3825404" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3825404" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3825404" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/12/chappell_mexico_lucha-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3825404" class="wp-caption-text"> Chappell Roan于2024年8月1日在伊利诺伊州芝加哥的Grant Park举行的Lollapalooza音乐节举行。 （图片由Erika Goldring/Wireimage）</figcaption></figure><p>佩里还告诉该出版物：“我不得不去寻找所有这些工具并治愈一些自己的东西。”</p><p>在其他新闻中，佩里将于1月30日与<a href="/artists/Billie-Eilish">Billie Eilish</a> ， <a href="/artists/Stevie-Nicks">Stevie Nicks</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/joni-mitchell">Joni Mitchell</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/red-hot-chili-peppers">Red Hot Chili Peppers</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sting">Sting</a> ，Sting， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/stevie-nicks">Stevie Nicks，Gracie Abrams</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gracie-abrams">Gracie Abrams，</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/green-day">Green Day</a> ，Green Day等人一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/stevie-wonder-the-black-crowes-anderson-paak-and-more-complete-fireaid-benefit-concert-line-up-3830921">在即将举行</a>的Fireeid Beady Face Concert演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/katy-perry-shares-music-industry-cheat-codes-she-gave-chappell-roan-and-doechii-for-handling-fame-3833042">凯蒂·佩里（Katy Perry）的邮政音乐行业“作弊代码”，她给了查佩尔·罗恩（Chappell Roan）和杜希（Doechii）处理名望，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
