e loading="lazy" title="妈妈 - 我想要你（发烧）（音乐视频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/WG0mAzP165o?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>在谈到这首歌时，乐队说：“&#39;我想要你（发烧）是我们写的一首歌，讲述了想和一个有女友或不结束前任的人在一起的歌曲。它正在追随某人，但也有一些信心知道那个人想和你在一起。第二张我们写了那首歌，我们觉得自己正在进入一个新时代 - 到目前为止，我们取消了我们为专辑写的一切，因为它感觉如此新鲜和令人兴奋。” </p><figure id="attachment_3833037" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3833037" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3833037" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="妈妈“欢迎来到我的蓝天”专辑插图。信用：出版" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Momma-Welcome-To-My-Blue-Sky-album-artwork.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3833037" class="wp-caption-text">妈妈“欢迎来到我的蓝天”专辑插图。信用：出版</figcaption></figure><h2><strong>“欢迎来到我的蓝天”曲目清单：</strong> </h2><ol><li data-leveltext="%1)" data-font="" data-listid=